feat: Add smart push notifications for session reminders

Implemented intelligent notification system with automated session reminders:

Smart Session Reminders:
- Automatic notifications at 2 hours, 1 hour, and 30 minutes before session
- scheduleSessionReminders() function for setting up all reminders
- cancelSessionReminders() to remove notifications when user leaves
- getScheduledSessionReminders() to view all scheduled notifications

Notification Types:
- Session reminders with time-based priority
- Achievement unlock notifications
- New message notifications
- Participant joined notifications

Integration:
- Auto-schedule reminders when participant is approved
- Notify session creator when new participant joins
- Uses Expo Notifications API for cross-platform support
- Proper error handling and logging

Features:
- High priority for 30-minute reminder
- Custom data payload for deep linking
- Sound and vibration support
- Android notification channels configured

